{"tid":1727733,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣入］諗到點大破廢老指有示威者背後金主沽港股之言論","createTime":"2019-11-16T14:10:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T14:12:16.000Z","uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1fa791a1f8fbab735cb7a29e2169ce522219a525","tid":1727733,"uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:10:44.000Z","msg":"廢老：「你班仆街仔，一定收咗金主錢搞亂香港，搞到股市跌。背後金主沽空港股賺錢，你哋醒下啦。」<br />\n<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已經唔想再講點派錢勒<br />\n<br />\n如果真係有背後金主沽空港股啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，政府答應示威者五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，以最快速度恢復秩序<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。咁利好消息股市實大升到仆街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲背後金主實輸到仆街啦，咁點解政府唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n答應五大訴求，香港一定贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17cece1ab8c71709449e3abe4c45ad037f9a6b05","tid":1727733,"uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:11:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e160c261d8efb7e7c351baa717638e0d7a6ec505","tid":1727733,"uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:11:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e590332aa8b9e53b2d2b0d4928bd5340cac5d4f0","tid":1727733,"uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:11:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3fa33d90395b6aceca4952fafb452d87ed5528","tid":1727733,"uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:12:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}